# Commits that changed formatting ONLY. `git blame` skips these so it still shows
# who last changed the LOGIC of a line, not who ran the formatter.
#
# Enable locally (once):
#   git config blame.ignoreRevsFile .git-blame-ignore-revs
# GitHub's blame view honours this file automatically.
#
# Only add a commit here if it is genuinely formatting-only. A commit that also
# changes behaviour must NOT be listed — it would hide a real author from blame.

